snippet.title: Void Dementia - Full Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Void Dementia on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1538640/Void_Dementia/

Void Dementia is characterized by fast action and hardcore production, and is an action game that will amplify the user's sense of challenge and immersion in the game with the story and Roguelike elements of the void area.
